snippet.title: Pulm Ex: Video Game for Pulmonologists
snippet.description:
Played by pulmonologists. Download Pulm Ex free from the App Store or Google Play.  https://level-ex.onelink.me/CMM6/youtube


Pulm Ex brings to life challenging patient cases that healthcare professionals can play to stay sharp in pulmonary medicine. The virtual bronchoscopy cases include foreign object removal, Cystic Fibrosis, HPV, Hamartoma, Hemoptysis, and Squamous Cell Carcinoma. A recent update to the game features two new levels, plus major visual enhancements.
